## Demo

Run `just demo` to populate fixture data and launch a Streamlit app showcasing all functionality. Every project should maintain a working demo that visually demonstrates what it can do.

The demo:
1. Runs `{{package_name}}.demo --setup` to populate a local data store with fixture data
2. Launches a Streamlit app at `src/{{package_name}}/demo_app.py`

When adding new features, update the demo to showcase them.

